        <title>Fair Treatment of Americans by Americans Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To ensure that, during time of war and in another country, the United States does not detain a United States citizen unless the United States first ensures that the citizen's fundamental rights to information, counsel, and communication are protected.</title>
      </item>
